          <p class='first-para'>
            I, too, shall be brief. There has not been such an outcry in Hampshire about health since the Government closed Lord Mayor Treloar's hospital in Alton. That hospital was doing excellent work, but in their centralising zeal the
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_78wh' title='Col. 78WH &mdash; HC Deb 22 January 2003 vol 398 c78WH' name='column_78wh' href='#column_78wh' rel='bookmark'>78WH</a>
